'''热带风暴费伊'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Fay}}）是一场在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]和[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]部分地区引发洪灾的中等强度热带风暴，也是[[2002年大西洋飓风季|2002年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第6场获得命名的风暴。2002年9月初，有[[低压槽|低压槽]]南下进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]并停止移动，其边缘发展出低气压中心，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机于9月5日发现系统已充分组织，在[[加尔维斯敦_(德克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]东南方向约153公里海域成为[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]<ref name="Fay 2002 report">{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | title = Tropical storm Fay Tropical Cyclone Report | year = 2002 | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2015-05-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304230155/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL062002_Fay.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL062002_Fay.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | date =  }}</ref>。气旋朝[[罗盘方位|西南偏南]]飘移并逐渐增强，于9月6日早上达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]95公里的最高强度<ref name="disc3">{{cite report | author = Beven | title = Tropical Storm Fay Discussion Number 3 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306140434/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.003.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.003.html | date =  }}</ref>。风暴接下来突然大幅向西北偏西转向，强度和朝向基本保持稳步，直至次日从德克萨斯州[[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]]的[[马塔哥达_(德克萨斯州)|马塔哥达]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="disc7">{{cite report | author = Lawrence | title = Tropical Storm Fay Discussion Number 8 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223743/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.008.html | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.008.html | date =  }}</ref>。费伊登陆后快速减弱，但其环流之后又持续三天才完全消散<ref name="Fay 2002 report" />。

气旋在陆地上产生大量降水，虽然没有引起人员丧生，但还是造成价值450万美元（2002年[[美元|美元]]）的破坏。<ref name="Fay 2002 report" />

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Fay 2002 track.png}}
2002年9月初，有[[低压槽|低压槽]]南下进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]后停止前进<ref name="Fay 2002 report" />，其边缘发展出[[雷暴|雷暴]]，并沿弱[[低气压|低气压]]系统集中。低压槽同关联的低气压逐渐向南飘移，进入墨西哥湾[[海面温度|水温]]较高的海域。位于墨西哥湾西北部的低气压区占据主导环流地位，并逐渐在中心附近发展出持续存在的[[对流|对流]]。9月5日，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机飞入系统后发现下层环流中心渐趋明朗，还有部分深层对流持续，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此将之归类成[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]。<ref name="Fay 2002 report" />墨西哥湾内此时[[风切变|风切变]]一直很少，有利于热带气旋形成<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Depression Six Discussion Number 1 | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.001.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002436/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.001.html | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。当晚侦察机又发现结构混乱的环流，导致气象机构不能很有把握地确定环流中心所在位置。不过，热带低气压内当晚已有足够对流持续，因此升级成热带风暴并获名“费伊”（{{lang|en|Fay}}）<ref name="disc2">{{cite report | author1 = Avila | author2 = Knabb | title = Tropical Storm Fay Discussion Number 2 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235859/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.002.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.002.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。

气旋接下来几乎停止移动，关联对流同环流中心分离，但强度仍在逐渐提高<ref name="disc3" /><ref name="disc41">{{cite report | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Fay Public Advisory Number 4 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al062002.public.004.html | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/pub/al062002.public.004.html | date =  }}</ref>。9月6日，风暴达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时95公里的最高强度，然后因少量风切变的限制而无法进一步强化，并因北侧的弱中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响逐渐恢复运动趋势<ref name="disc3" /><ref name="disc41" />。南面的低气压系统产生风切变，导致费伊南半部环流内的对流消退，大部分对流局限在北部半圆中<ref name="disc4">{{cite report | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Fay Discussion Number 4 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233205/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.004.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.004.html | date =  }}</ref>。气旋很快就变得杂乱无章，气象机构在公告中称费伊此时更象是[[亚热带气旋|亚热带风暴]]<ref name="disc5">{{cite report | author = Avila | title = Tropical Storm Fay Discussion Number 6 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.006.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002081125/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.006.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。风暴接下来的移动幅度很小，9月6日晚还略有增强<ref name="disc5" /><ref name="disc29">{{cite report | author = Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Fay Discussion Number 5 | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303201449/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.005.html | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.005.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。

9月7日，费伊开始朝西北方向的[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]海岸前进，雨带行进至该州西北部海岸线<ref name="disc6">{{cite report | author = Pasch | title = Tropical Storm Fay Discussion Number 7 | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.007.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225039/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2002/dis/al062002.discus.007.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。气旋加速移动，于当天清晨[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。进入内陆上空后，风暴的移动速度放缓，方向飘忽不定，很快就降级成热带低气压。美国国家飓风中心于9月7日发布针对费伊的最后一份公告，但系统此后在距德克萨斯州海岸不远的陆地上空又持续了数天才完全消散。<ref name="disc7"/><ref name="HPC">{{cite report | author = Hydrological Prediction Center | title = Tropical Storm Fay Advisory Number 9 | year = 2002 | work = Weather Prediction Center | publisher = National Centers for Environmental Prediction | 6 =  | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090606/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=FAY&adnum=17&dt=2002090921&status=remnants | location = [[大学公园市|College Park]], [[马里兰州|Maryland]] | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/tropical_advisories.php?storm=FAY&adnum=17&dt=2002090921&status=remnants | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>

== 防灾措施 ==
系统成为热带低气压时，气象部门就向德克萨斯州部分沿海地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="disc1" />。气旋升级成热带风暴后，警告生效范围从马塔哥达（{{lang|en|Matagorda}}）延伸到[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]沿海地区。9月8日，气象机构又把警告范围延伸到德克萨斯州[[阿兰萨斯港_(德克萨斯州)|阿兰萨斯港]]（{{lang|en|Port Aransas}}），同时因气象部门预计费伊登陆前会达到飓风强度，该州[[卡尔霍恩县_(德克萨斯州)|卡尔霍恩县]][[奥康纳港_(德克萨斯州)|奥康纳港]]（{{lang|en|Port O'Connor}}）到[[加尔维斯顿县|加尔维斯顿县]][[高岛_(德克萨斯州)|高岛]]（{{lang|en|High Island}}）地区也接获飓风观察预警。之后风暴未达飓风标准，上述飓风观察预警因此中止。<ref name="Fay 2002 report" />此外，德克萨斯州和路易斯安那州沿海地区还进入[[沿海洪灾警告|沿海洪灾警告]]生效状态<ref name="HPC" />，德克萨斯州部分内陆地区收到山洪警告和洪灾警告<ref name="HPC" />。

面对风暴威胁，加尔维斯顿和高岛的多所学校在9月6日关闭，有关部门还向沿海低洼地区发布自愿撤离令<ref name="USA Today 3">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | title = Fay Spins off Galveston, sends rain, wind ashore | publisher = Gannett | work = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019201221/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2002/2002-09-06-fay.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/news/2002/2002-09-06-fay.htm | date = 2002-09-15 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 }}</ref>。[[布拉佐里亚县|布拉佐里亚县]]县城[[安格尔顿_(德克萨斯州)|安格尔顿]]（{{lang|en|Angleton}}）有多家杂货店出现商品短缺<ref name="thefacts">{{cite news | author = Bridie Isensee | title = Residents in no apparent hurry to stock up | year = 2003 | publisher = The Facts | accessdate = 2008-09-10 | url = http://stories.thefacts.com/story.lasso?wcd=9034 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080910022516/http://stories.thefacts.com/story.lasso?wcd=9034 | archivedate = 2008-09-10 }}</ref>。

== 影响 ==
[[File:Fay_2002_rainfall.gif|right]]
路易斯安那州和[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]所受很小，基本局限于中等程度降水，最高降雨量达到76毫米<ref name="disc31">{{cite report | author = Hydrological Prediction Center | title = Tropical Storm Fay - September 4-14, 2002 | year = 2002 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065507/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/fay2002.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/fay2002.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。

德克萨斯州部分地区受到中至重度破坏，其中大部分都是由洪水引起。该州共有400套房屋因洪灾受损<ref name="2002 MWR">{{cite report | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Miles B. Lawrence | author3 = Lixion A. Avila | author4 = John L. Beven | author5 = James L. Franklin | author6 = Stacy R. Stewart | title = 2002 Atlantic hurricane season | year = 2002 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303195251/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/2002.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/2002.pdf | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref><ref name="Red Cross">{{cite news | author = Mason Anderson | title = Tropical Storm Fay strikes south Texas | year = 2002 | publisher = [[国际红十字与红新月运动|Red cross]] | accessdate = 2008-12-03 | url = http://www.redcross.org/news/ds/floods/020909texas.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081203055255/http://www.redcross.org/news/ds/floods/020909texas.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2008-12-03 }}</ref>。费伊登陆时催生出一场[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]，对[[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]]最北端海岸沿线构成轻度破坏<ref name="NCDC">{{cite report | author = NCDC | title = Event-tornado September 6 | year = 2002 | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2011-05-20 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~479857 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110520001637/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~479857 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2011-05-20 | date =  }}</ref>。德克萨斯州海岸沿线的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]有1.1米高<ref name="disc30">{{cite news | author = Joel Roberts | title = Tropical storm Fay fades as it moves inland | publisher = [[CBS互动|CBS Interactive]] | work = [[CBS新闻|CBS News]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120309180932/http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2002/09/06/national/main521047.shtml | accessdate = 2016-05-25 | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/fay-fading-hits-land-weakens/ | date = 2002-09-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-03-09 }}</ref>，州内各地的最高降雨量在250至380毫米之间<ref name="disc30" />。布拉佐里亚县的[[斯维尼_(德克萨斯州)|斯维尼]]（{{lang|en|Sweeny}}）受到风暴重创，共有约1000户民宅和商铺受损，损失数额约为350万美元（2002年美元）。高达600毫米的雨量在当地及周边地区引发严重山洪。[[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]]也因费伊遭受重大破坏，该县道路及公共设施因洪灾导致的损失数额约有130万美元（2002年美元）<ref name="Fay 2002 report" />。

据报导，气旋登陆期间催生出12场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，其中最具影响的一场导致一套移动房屋被毁，另有一个谷仓受损<ref name="Fay 2002 report" />。费伊的残留在[[弗里奥县_(德克萨斯州)|弗里奥县]]降下50至75毫米雨量，[[亚他斯科沙县|亚他斯科沙县]]测得200毫米降水，局部地区达到300毫米。暴雨引发严重山洪，许多人被迫躲到屋顶上。上述两县的建筑、道路和农作物一共受到价值80万美元（2002年美元）的破坏。<ref name="disc21">{{cite report | author = NCDC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080904081601/http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~479896 | title = Event-flooding September 8 | year = 2002 | publisher = NOAA | accessdate = 2008-01-03 | archivedate = 2008-09-04 | url = http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~479896 | deadurl = yes | date =  }}</ref>

费伊对墨西哥的影响总体局限于降水，部分地点的降雨量达到400毫米<ref name="disc31" />。[[塔毛利帕斯州|塔毛利帕斯州]]的[[新拉雷多|新拉雷多]]爆发洪灾，约100户家庭从家中转移，还有120人被困在酒店。据报导，该市有十棵树木倒塌，但破坏程度非常轻微。[[格兰德河|格兰德河]]的河水超出洪水水位3.3米之多。受洪灾影响，有约300户家庭之后数周都无法返回家园。<ref>{{cite news | author = CDI | title = Los pueblos indígenas en la prensa nacional | publisher = Instituto Nacional Indigenista | year = 2002 | accessdate = 2008-04-09 | url = http://www.cdi.gob.mx/ini/noticias/11-sep-02.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070717110435/http://cdi.gob.mx/ini/noticias/11-sep-02.html | archivedate = 2007-07-17 }}</ref>

== 善后 ==
风暴过后，德克萨斯州有九个县（分别是布拉佐里亚县、弗里奥县、加尔维斯顿县、[[拉萨尔县_(德克萨斯州)|拉萨尔县]]、[[来弗欧克县|来弗欧克县]]、马塔哥达县、[[努埃塞斯县_(得克萨斯州)|努埃塞斯县]]、[[圣帕特里西奥县_(得克萨斯州)|圣帕特里西奥县]]和[[霍顿县_(得克萨斯州)|霍顿县]]）经宣告成为灾区，以便受灾居民及企业主申请联邦及州政府援助<ref name="disc23">{{cite news | title = FEMA Declared Counties | year = 2002 | publisher = [[联邦紧急事务管理局|Federal Emergency Management Agency]] | accessdate = 2012-02-18 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/eventcounties.fema?id=161 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120218081551/http://www.fema.gov/news/eventcounties.fema?id=161 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-02-18 }}</ref><ref name="disc11">{{cite news | title = Tropical storm Fay news release | year = 2002 | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | accessdate = 2012-02-18 | archivedate = 2012-02-18 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120218081637/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=739 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=739 }}</ref>。费伊过去后，救灾机构共计签发数值超过270万美元（2002年美元）的灾害住民补贴支票，[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]已检查过超过2700套各类民宅和建筑物。包括个人及家庭补助计划在内的多种非政府救灾方案共计通过支票向灾民提供40万美元救助金和超过100万美元的救灾资金。[[小企业管理局|小企业管理局]]也拨出超过25万美元的救灾援助金。<ref name="disc24">{{cite news | title = Disaster Assistance Update for Ten Counties Affected by Tropical Storm Fay | year = 2002 | publisher = Federal Emergency Management Agency | accessdate = 2012-02-18 | url = http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=3904 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120218081640/http://www.fema.gov/news/newsrelease.fema?id=3904 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-02-18 }}</ref>[[美国国家税务局|美国国家税务局]]在气旋过去后宣布，德克萨斯州沦为灾区的九个县可以获得特殊税收减免<ref>{{cite news |author=[[美国国家税务局|IRS]] |title=Tax relief to Tropical Storm Fay victims |year=2002 |accessdate=2011-10-20 |archivedate=2011-10-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111020051543/http://www.irs.gov/newsroom/article/0%2C%2Cid%3D106054%2C00.html |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.irs.gov/newsroom/article/0,,id=106054,00.html }}</ref>。

